    SIL Open Font License 1.1 — see https://scripts.sil.org/OFL
    Reserved Font Name: "Fira Code"
  - Patched glyphs: Nerd Fonts by Ryan L McIntyre (ryanoasis/nerd-fonts)
    MIT License
  - Web build (woff2): mshaugh/nerdfont-webfonts redistribution
