Code samples
------------

Zig source blocks shown on the home page (CredentialLiveness +
Availability, DegradedReason + DeadReason, MuxDecision +
fromHttpStatus) are reproduced verbatim from
github.com/Jesssullivan/oauth-mux at src/types.zig (MIT, same author).

Verbatim quoted ranges live in src/lib/content/cli-examples.ts as
ZIG_LIVENESS_BLOCK, ZIG_DEAD_DEGRADED, and ZIG_MUX_DECISION exports.

Shiki theme
-----------

Code highlighting uses the Vitesse light/dark themes by Anthony Fu
(MIT) bundled with shiki@4.x. No theme file is committed to this
repository; Shiki resolves them at build time.
